Package: topPolluters
Type: Package
Title: Top Climate, Air, and Water Polluters (2018)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Michael Ash <mash@econs.umass.edu>
Maintainer: Alyssa <alyandric@reed.edu> , Blaise <albisbub@reed.edu>
Description: This data set lists the top 100 polluter companies by the comparative risk they pose to chronic human health from air pollutants directly released or transferred to incinerators (and not destroyed) from large facilities in the US in 2018. The authors acknowledge the Political Economy Research Institute at the University of Massachusetts for providing data that have contributed to the research results reported within this project.
Encoding: UTF-8
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 2.10),dplyr
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1



